Official Java client for the validation of YubiKey OTPs, consisting of
https://github.com/Yubico/yubico-java-client/tree/master/v2client[the Java client] and an optional
https://github.com/Yubico/yubico-java-client/tree/master/jaas[module for integration with JAAS].

If you want the client for the legacy version 1 of the API, it can be found https://github.com/Yubico/yubico-java-client/tree/master/v1client[here].